<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٩٤٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6983">يَحْيَى بْنُ قَزَعَةَ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3384">عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ الْقَاسِمِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5159">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3431">عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5417">وَمُجَمِّعٍ ابْنَيْ يَزِيدَ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بْنِ جَارِيَةَ الْأَنْصَارِيِّ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1830">خَنْسَاءَ بِنْتِ خِذَامٍ الْأَنْصَارِيَّةِ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ أَبَاهَا زَوَّجَهَا وَهِيَ ثَيِّبٌ فَكَرِهَتْ ذَلِكَ، فَأَتَتِ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَرَدَّ نِكَاحَهَا.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>